# Live meeting dirs are timestamped YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM-* — local-only by default.
# To track a specific meeting (e.g. an archived reference), force-add it
# with `git add -f meetings/<dir>`.
/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-*/

# LaTeX build artifacts under any sample / fixture dir.
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.pdf
